02:52.000 --> 02:56.000
also the participants and the person responsible for the business process of the client of this process,

02:56.000 --> 03:01.000
and the participants and the person responsible for the supplier of this process.

03:02.000 --> 03:06.000
We give them a questionnaire and they fill it in.

03:06.000 --> 03:12.000
Usually, they give the importance of this particular process by 5 or 10-point system.

03:12.000 --> 03:17.000
Intuitively, by their own methods.

03:17.000 --> 03:23.000
For example, if you assess the importance of the business process of the trade of clothes,

03:24.000 --> 03:29.000
you can invite the head of the process,

03:29.000 --> 03:35.000
the participants, the manager of the purchases, the production, the sales,

03:35.000 --> 03:38.000
the representatives of the client,

03:38.000 --> 03:41.000
the suppliers,

03:41.000 --> 03:46.000
and you can invite several more employees of your company,

03:46.000 --> 03:50.000
