03:51.000 --> 03:54.000
because they also participate in this business process,

03:54.000 --> 03:57.000
and, accordingly, from the marketing department,

03:57.000 --> 04:02.000
the head, who also participates in this business process at the time of sale,

04:02.000 --> 04:10.000
