The most important and key problems described in the strategy,

01:04:31.000 --> 01:04:35.000
the most important strategic goals,

01:04:35.000 --> 01:04:39.000
and the most important indicators to achieve the strategic goals outlined in the company.

01:04:39.000 --> 01:04:43.000
Next.

01:04:43.000 --> 01:04:47.000
We had one client who decided to introduce such a KPI

