01:05:47.000 --> 01:05:51.000
If you do not have the appropriate channels, probably not.

01:05:51.000 --> 01:05:55.000
Therefore, no matter how great the KPI is,

01:05:55.000 --> 01:05:59.000
you should not have such a KPI.

01:05:59.000 --> 01:06:03.000
You should not have such a KPI,

01:06:03.000 --> 01:06:07.000
which will include a lot of additional indicators,

01:06:07.000 --> 01:06:11.000
and as a result, you will get confused

01:06:11.000 --> 01:06:15.000
what to multiply and what to divide.

01:06:15.000 --> 01:06:19.000
As a result, your KPI will be considered

01:06:19.000 --> 01:06:23.000
with a large number of errors.

01:06:23.000 --> 01:06:27.000
Therefore, do not complicate the calculation of the KPI.

01:06:27.000 --> 01:06:31.000
You should be sure that the owner of the business process

01:06:31.000 --> 01:06:35.000
