01:06:43.000 --> 01:06:47.000
of managers who worked with clients,

01:06:47.000 --> 01:06:51.000
that is, sellers.

01:06:51.000 --> 01:06:55.000
All this is great, but in the sales department

01:06:55.000 --> 01:06:59.000
the owner of the business process

01:06:59.000 --> 01:07:03.000
