01:07:07.000 --> 01:07:11.000
where to carry them in terms of primary documentation,

01:07:11.000 --> 01:07:15.000
what terms, what information to provide to the accounting department.

01:07:15.000 --> 01:07:19.000
Therefore, it was impossible to introduce such a KPI

01:07:19.000 --> 01:07:23.000
to this business process.

01:07:23.000 --> 01:07:27.000
