01:08:07.000 --> 01:08:11.000
In other words, there should not be any side-effects.

01:08:11.000 --> 01:08:15.000
You should be sure that the process is improving

01:08:15.000 --> 01:08:19.000
not due to the deterioration of some other indicators,

01:08:19.000 --> 01:08:23.000
