01:08:59.000 --> 01:09:03.000
As a result, they reduced the cost of glass storage,

01:09:03.000 --> 01:09:07.000
but at the same time they increased the costs for the staff.

01:09:07.000 --> 01:09:11.000
As a result, the effect was not even zero,

01:09:11.000 --> 01:09:15.000
but negative.

01:09:15.000 --> 01:09:19.000
So, the KPIs should be balanced.

