01:13:29.000 --> 01:13:33.000
Or there is a controversial point,

01:13:33.000 --> 01:13:37.000
or it is necessary to change the current course of the business process.

01:13:37.000 --> 01:13:41.000
For these purposes, the Regulation is needed.

01:13:41.000 --> 01:13:45.000
It fixes a certain agreement

01:13:45.000 --> 01:13:49.000
between employees and companies

01:13:49.000 --> 01:13:53.000
on who behaves.

01:13:53.000 --> 01:13:57.000
This agreement is the tool

01:13:57.000 --> 01:14:01.000
of the influence of the boss on his subordinates.

01:14:01.000 --> 01:14:05.000
And what is written in the Regulation,

01:14:05.000 --> 01:14:09.000
the employee must do.

01:14:09.000 --> 01:14:13.000
If he does not do this,

01:14:13.000 --> 01:14:17.000
he does not comply with the agreement,

01:14:17.000 --> 01:14:21.000
and some punitive measures may be applied for this.

01:14:21.000 --> 01:14:25.000
And he will not be able to comply with the Regulation.

01:14:25.000 --> 01:14:29.000
The Regulation will allow you to make your company transparent.

01:14:29.000 --> 01:14:33.000
It will be clear who is responsible for what,

01:14:33.000 --> 01:14:37.000
what functions are responsible.

01:14:37.000 --> 01:14:41.000
Regulations can be developed not only for specific employees,

01:14:41.000 --> 01:14:45.000
as is often the case.

01:14:45.000 --> 01:14:49.000
They are developed at the corporate level,

01:14:49.000 --> 01:14:53.000
then at the department level,

01:14:53.000 --> 01:14:57.000
and finally at the employees' level.

01:14:57.000 --> 01:15:01.000
Therefore, Regulations are an integral part of the management process.

01:15:01.000 --> 01:15:05.000
What are Regulations?

01:15:05.000 --> 01:15:09.000
I think that each of you has a certain Regulation.

01:15:09.000 --> 01:15:13.000
Most often, 90% of cases,

01:15:13.000 --> 01:15:17.000
you have a structural Regulation.

01:15:17.000 --> 01:15:21.000
It is a kind of a system of regulations

01:15:21.000 --> 01:15:25.000
that is defined by the department,

01:15:25.000 --> 01:15:29.000
by the employees, by the departments,

01:15:29.000 --> 01:15:33.000
by the departments,

01:15:33.000 --> 01:15:37.000
by the departments,

01:15:37.000 --> 01:15:41.000
by the departments,

01:15:41.000 --> 01:15:45.000
by the departments,

01:15:45.000 --> 01:15:49.000
by the departments.

01:15:49.000 --> 01:15:53.000
Regulations are a kind of a system of rules

01:15:53.000 --> 01:15:57.000
that allow everybody to understand

01:15:57.000 --> 01:16:01.000
what processes are carried out in the company,

01:16:01.000 --> 01:16:05.000
on what conditions and on what rules they should be carried out.

01:16:05.000 --> 01:16:09.000
If a person comes to your company,

01:16:09.000 --> 01:16:13.000
