01:16:17.000 --> 01:16:21.000
and for what purpose it will happen,

01:16:21.000 --> 01:16:25.000
because the result will be clear.

01:16:25.000 --> 01:16:29.000
And then he will receive a specific instruction

01:16:29.000 --> 01:16:33.000
