01:16:33.000 --> 01:16:37.000
This will be the structure of regulations.

01:16:37.000 --> 01:16:41.000
Thus, the process regulation allows you to understand

01:16:41.000 --> 01:16:45.000
the structure of the company.

01:16:45.000 --> 01:16:49.000
If we look at the structure of regulations in any company,

01:16:49.000 --> 01:16:53.000
let's say, we are talking about the structure of regulations,

01:16:53.000 --> 01:16:57.000
then the position in the organization is the highest level document.

01:16:57.000 --> 01:17:01.000
Then the position in the department,

01:17:01.000 --> 01:17:05.000
then in the department, and then the official instruction.

01:17:05.000 --> 01:17:09.000
If we move on to the process system of management,

01:17:09.000 --> 01:17:13.000
we will see that there are three main structures for the process system of regulation.

01:17:13.000 --> 01:17:17.000
The first one is the position on the business processes of the highest level.

01:17:17.000 --> 01:17:21.000
