01:18:31.000 --> 01:18:35.000
They are written in such a way that you don't want to do anything but cry when you look at them.

01:18:39.000 --> 01:18:43.000
You can only execute them from under the stick.

01:18:43.000 --> 01:18:47.000
Therefore, the document must be readable.

01:18:47.000 --> 01:18:51.000
Include schemes of business processes, normal interval,

01:18:51.000 --> 01:18:55.000
responsibilities, additional drawings.

01:18:55.000 --> 01:18:59.000
It must be readable.

01:18:59.000 --> 01:19:03.000
The more we include in this document, the better.

01:19:03.000 --> 01:19:07.000
It must be a clear structure and maximum usefulness for the user of this instruction or other regulations.

01:19:11.000 --> 01:19:15.000
The contradiction.

01:19:15.000 --> 01:19:19.000
Very often, when we get acquainted with the documentation of a specific client,

01:19:19.000 --> 01:19:23.000
