01:19:31.000 --> 01:19:35.000
I don't know where you got this instruction from, it's from the forgotten times.

01:19:35.000 --> 01:19:39.000
Therefore, the instructions, all regulations must be mutually exclusive.

01:19:39.000 --> 01:19:43.000
If your business process is described in a certain way,

01:19:43.000 --> 01:19:47.000
