01:20:25.000 --> 01:20:29.000
Then we will talk about processes, then about specific operations.

01:20:29.000 --> 01:20:33.000
No other way.

01:20:33.000 --> 01:20:37.000
Next, if you have agreed to the regulations,

01:20:37.000 --> 01:20:41.000
