01:20:45.000 --> 01:20:49.000
This is not what you wrote and put on the shelf,

01:20:49.000 --> 01:20:53.000
otherwise it will be the same fate as in the current documentation.

01:20:53.000 --> 01:20:57.000
You will have to ask them regularly to implement this specific regulation.

01:20:57.000 --> 01:21:01.000
And for this control, you will need the same KPI that you have developed in the previous step.

01:21:05.000 --> 01:21:09.000
