01:21:21.000 --> 01:21:25.000
That is, we have ideally located the responsible and the executors,

01:21:25.000 --> 01:21:29.000
then we have created the process structure and the structural regulation,

01:21:29.000 --> 01:21:33.000
and then we start to implement it all and have a normal working organization at the output.

01:21:37.000 --> 01:21:41.000
If we list the main requirements for regulation,

01:21:41.000 --> 01:21:45.000
then it is imperative to set the level of regulation,

01:21:45.000 --> 01:21:49.000
again, to clearly specify the name of each regulation,

01:21:49.000 --> 01:21:53.000
for example, the status of the structure, the status of the department,

01:21:53.000 --> 01:21:57.000
the status of the department, the status of the official instruction.

